dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"總之，現在唔好再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲嬲豬喇"},{"pid":"4f62dbdc379e1a7531e59d7b08e8ef3e4d4e805b","tid":1954684,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f143bf154937881050574c33fb91d6454eed3791","tid":1954684,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"比記者chok多兩chok就認專欄純虛構9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"好多網台當笑話講佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43de3fd3fd8cb35a4ac7b9af1ee5ade58e33d896","tid":1954684,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01deb5ebd5189aa740463a629fb70b5f743cdbd6","tid":1954684,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"一世靠家姐既垃圾<br />\n<br />\n本身係廢人一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"佢真人真係幾廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115e491442986d5f65bf03a2a9ea525275423b21","tid":1954684,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又欺騙讀者<br />\n<br />\n入福布斯叫-廖湯慧靄 而唔係呢條垃圾</span><br />\n<br />\n作者簡介：<br />\n<br />\n湯文亮博士<br />\n紀惠集團行政總裁，資深地產投資者，縱橫樓市30多年，集團在本港持有物業市值總值達數百億元，<span style=\"color: red;\">並在2017年開始打進《福布斯》香港富豪排行榜，2019年最新排名第25位。</span> 同時也是活躍的專欄作家，在財經雜誌《Money Monday》、《i-money智富雜誌》、《明報》及《蘋果日報》等均有其專欄。由2011年開始在「Yahoo! 地產」撰寫Blog，點擊率超過2億人次，現於「<a href=\"http://m.property.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.property.hk&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=48b8352b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.property.hk</a>」、「NOW地產」、「PropNew潮流主場」及「橙」都有撰寫文章。湯博士在澳門出生及長大，後赴加拿大留學，曾獲第13屆傑出華人獎，並先後出版《辣招如何扭曲樓市》、《破解樓市之謎》等10本暢銷書籍。"},{"pid":"e5532bd66341cd7aff43b84c0d2fce455ecd075d","tid":1954684,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"唔係男人黎<br />\n講得出又唔敢認<br />\n切撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"f0073a8f72f944762b8b56f977b3e7181c2171de","tid":1954684,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5532bd66341cd7aff43b84c0d2fce455ecd075d","tid":1954684,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"唔係男人黎<br />\n講得出又唔敢認<br />\n切撚左佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"佢邊有唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲大搖大擺話自己作故仔亂up"}]}